Somehow it all adds up. Way back before and behind and beyond all these comparatively recent languages,

there must lurk, I fondly hoped, one universal pararnt tongue, which contains the great simultaneous equation:

big equals good and small equals bad. Triumph!

By why am I burdening your with my private game playing? This less than scientific speculation, it's hardly what a liguist will call authentic.

